@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lawbsp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (((v0 + 0.38 / v1 + 0.73) + 0.18) / 0.76)
    tmp = ((0.46 / 0.36) * wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.76)))
    v2 = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.05 - v0 + 0.77) * (v0 + 0.05 - v2 + 0.66)))
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
